description: The fund invests primarily in a diversified portfolio of U.S. dollar-denominated high-yield fixed income instruments. The adviser selects instruments, including securities, that the adviser believes have attractive risk-return characteristics. The fund will invest its assets so that at least 80% of its net assets (plus any borrowings for investment purposes) are invested in investments rated below investment-grade.
name: Federated Hermes Short Duration High Yield ETF
